g.text: Belinda bunny was a happy, fluffy bunny who loves wintertime. She
enjoys hopping around and playing in the snow! But one day she noticed
her friend, Benji had a sad look on his face. Benji said his friends had left
him out of their game and he was feeling sad and not loved. Belinda said
to Benji “I know! Let’s practice our Bunny Breath to feel silly and happy!”
So they took three Bunny Breaths together, and then ran off to play and
hop around in the snow. Thank you Belinda for connecting with Benji,
being a kind friend, and remembering how fun it is to be silly and bring
